\f1\fs48 \cf2 First Things First\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl420\sa280

\f0\fs28 \cf3 Welcome. WordPress is a very special project to me. Every developer and contributor adds something unique to the mix, and together we create something beautiful that I'm proud to be a part of. Thousands of hours have gone into WordPress, and we're dedicated to making it better every day. Thank you for making it part of your world.\
